# Togglable

If you don't want to manage your modal open state at all, use the toggable version.

    W.Modal.viewToggable []
        { id = "toggable-modal"
        , content = [ text "Hello!" ]
        }

    W.Modal.viewToggle "toggable-modal"
        [ W.Button.viewDummy []
            [ text "Click here to toggle modal" ]
        ]

